{"tid":444023,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"毒L問點買starbucks","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T01:37:12.000Z","uid":136553,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ed72846d621422278ebad2e4f1028d5e9c5d7ed8","tid":444023,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"學校送左兩張starbucks禮券<br />\n想試下買<br />\n但又唔知點買法<br />\n講中文定英文？<br />\n同埋買邊隻咖啡好？求教"},{"pid":"901dfd740cb72be2954fc0382ef26f3cb4558708","tid":444023,"uid":91203,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:05:30.000Z","msg":"要講英文 落order時記得話比佢聽自己喺Mr咩 因為佢要叫你攞嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘢飲推薦Pearl milk tea"},{"pid":"234828c673853f1f1afaf25e71e4ea017498c8e2","tid":444023,"uid":39428,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"講中文算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdba5ed9f649e7c846ea6577d8c1138bc1add78a","tid":444023,"uid":43536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"本來諗住叫你用APP買，不過你用禮券就去counter買級不千奴啦"},{"pid":"5b4da94d87814dc7add692389d68b201f4782369","tid":444023,"uid":53254,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"this, one, nonono, this, yes, thanks"},{"pid":"43920ca7d94e66f7c8c53923027ee1b5d4515ec7","tid":444023,"uid":36673,"like":14,"dislike":10,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n啞既話對住個餐牌指就得，其實中英文都得，旺角個間通用中文多（之前新個杯，會問番「要茶定沙冰？」）<br />\n最低買grande（中杯？），tall好細杯下但只差幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">熱飲飲開，不過可以轉凍<br />\nHot latte (唔甜) / caramel macchiato (甜) / matcha latte (港女抹茶) / chai tea latte (香料奶茶) / hot chocolate (冬天飲正)<br />\n<br />\n凍野通常沙冰，正d，沙冰=Frappuccino<br />\nCoffee / Matcha cream/ chocolate chips / <br />\nMango passion fruit </span>"},{"pid":"caf26e0ba2ec11999a18cfb30cdc46655b723448","ti